        "content": "## Sub - Social - Claude API Call\n\n**Input:**\n- prompt (required)\n- system_prompt (optional)\n- max_tokens (default: 4096)\n- temperature (default: 0.7)\n- model (default: claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929)\n\n**Output:**\n- response\n- tokens_used\n- input_tokens\n- output_tokens\n- model\n- success\n- error (if failed)"
      },
